<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 cōng míng rén bǎ fáng zi gài zài pán shí shàng, wú zhī de rén bǎ fáng zi gài zài shā tǔ shàng.
 yǔ lín shuǐ chōng fēng chuī zhuàng zhe nà fáng zi, nǎ zuò fáng zi huì dào tā xīn zhōng dōu míng liàng.
 tīng jiàn zhǔ de huà qù xíng shì zài pán shí shàng, tīng jiàn zhǔ de huà bù xíng shì zài shā tǔ shàng.
 liǎng děng gēn jī liǎng zhǒng jiàn zào liǎng gè bǐ fāng, zhǔ de jiào dǎo yào shēn shēn sī xiǎng.</lyrics>
<title>liǎng děng gēn jī 迦南1161</title>
<hymn_number>1161</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>